---
title: Spicy Crusted Hake and Baby Corn with creamy mashed potato
description: A hearty spoon of velvety mashed potato sits alongside pan-fried covered in a spicy cheese coating in this recipe. Tender baby corn and a sprinkling of vibrant chives round out an exciting and nourishing weeknight meal.
